@DATABASE "Byte Bitten"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Byte Bitten"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                                Byte Bitten
                                ===========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(53429,0)"}          53429,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43358,255)"}          43358,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52790,0)"}          52790,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
